msgstr "`webAuthn.register` 方法会调用注册挑战端点，随后调用身份验证器并调用该注册对应的注册端点，最后返回一个 link:https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise[Promise 对象] ："

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-webauthn.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Invoke login"
msgstr "调用登录"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-webauthn.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `webAuthn.login` method invokes the login challenge endpoint, then calls the authenticator and invokes the login endpoint\n"
"for that login, and returns a https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise[Promise object]:"
msgstr "`webAuthn.login` 方法会调用登录挑战端点，随后调用身份验证器并调用该登录对应的登录端点，最后返回一个 link:https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise[Promise 对象] ："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-webauthn.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The username is optional, in the case of https://www.w3.org/TR/webauthn-3/#discoverable-credential[Discoverable Credentials] (with PassKeys)"
msgstr "对于 link:https://www.w3.org/TR/webauthn-3/#discoverable-credential[可发现凭据] （带 PassKeys），用户名是可选的"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-webauthn.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Only invoke the registration challenge and authenticator"
