#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-webauthn.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `webAuthn.registerClientSteps` method invokes the registration challenge endpoint, then calls the authenticator and returns\n"
